{"tid":1517234,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［新戰線］返/放工向敵方罵陣！","createTime":"2019-08-30T01:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T01:30:26.000Z","uid":258339,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e6a3b54935418140a95cc0b1ad252fb217bf20ec","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:10:24.000Z","msg":"是咁的，岩岩返工，見到樓下有民建聯擺街站為嚟緊區議會選舉拉票，個易拉架上仲寫住「守護孩子，反對罷課」咁。<br />\n<br />\n我份人好有禮貌，就算cut唔到有線都無嬲過，但當我諗到<span style=\"color: red;\">前線咁多手足被捕被虐，擺上前途</span>嘅時候，我見到民建聯就無名火起！<br />\n<br />\n於是面懵懵走上前，話下佢地「出賣下一代，民建聯食屎...」。我真心有啲淆，好細聲，但與此同時，隔離啲街坊竟然一齊加把口話「你地無良心呀」、「一票不投民建聯」、「民建聯賣港」等等。但派傳單呀姨都唔弱，仲反擊，話班街坊「你地先係垃圾！」，之後有個呀姐好正，鬧返佢「食傻食糉咗你呀？」，個一下真係好溫暖，原來大家咁團結、齊心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">重點：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n有鑑於10點9叫活動非常成功，小弟係到建議，大家返工放工/返學放學，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">見到民建聯擺街站、派傳單等等任何形式活動，都唔好放過狙擊佢地嘅機會，盡自己最大努力鬧爆佢！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我相信除左可以令呢班契弟帶來前所未有嘅壓力，減少蒲頭外，仲有帶風向作用，令其他街坊就算唔知投邊個，但知道唔投佢地就啱！<br />\n<br />\n另外，認真，我唔建議使用暴力，呢場係輿論陣地戰，出手會非常吃虧<br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊討論更多可行性<br />\n<br />\n祝大家口運昌隆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驅走共黨</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">光復香港</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"d1f6914a896a1f9caf54e28fc1ea22e36bd97d19","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:12:00.000Z","msg":"P牌仔無力一推"},{"pid":"65069b5d69a88b273f9a7d8fc6d9ae42849bee43","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c67e1ef7898326afbd75e27f433b9be6b52210ba","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08330b2cb76e8f01774c27866a5178e7844323c2","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:14:05.000Z","msg":"有無甩P人仕，歡迎隨便偷文"},{"pid":"7f53d6ab6af5fc76c8d4bc46e02bfc8d8c23c779","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:14:24.000Z","msg":"俾多啲人見到就可以"},{"pid":"287d5f62c3285cd38347045517fb5aa590cec9c8","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:14:48.000Z","msg":"黑"},{"pid":"603015831acc589c967011aa25dfc34d484de6ea","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:15:01.000Z","msg":"驚"},{"pid":"aa942efd4915a6a93c7b2d3e213b5b155c78734b","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:15:11.000Z","msg":"死"},{"pid":"2f5be0cf2bb62abe4cc47e7b031c8fb6dc38838d","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:15:22.000Z","msg":"全"},{"pid":"63bb7b5e6d410d9addbdd5f99faa4eb5b8a16b00","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:15:32.000Z","msg":"家"},{"pid":"34fcc1eca1769553c6a334dd6e2c49b16e7d31fe","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:15:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4b7efcc1175883848a7ede4075a659c9e68b101","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2c1a3db87389d44552f06b6c8baa9f3e020910c","tid":1517234,"uid":258339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T01:16:26.000Z","msg":"單機